boxing day is a secular holiday celebrated the day after christmas day . 
boxing day is a secular holiday that is traditionally celebrated on 26 december ,  the day after christmas day . 
in australia ,  boxing day is a public holiday in all jurisdictions except the australian state of south australia where a public holiday known as proclamation day is celebrated on the first weekday after christmas day or the christmas day holiday . 
boxing day is on 26 december ,  although the attached bank holiday or public holiday may take place either on that day or two days later . 
in canada ,  boxing day is a federal statutory holiday . 
26 december is also saint stephen's day ,  a religious holiday . 
balochistan  -lrb-  ;   -rrb-   is one of the four provinces of pakistan . 
balochistan is situated in the southwest of pakistan and covers an area of  . 
during the caliphate of ali ,  revolt broke out in southern balochistan's makran region . 
two devastating earthquakes occurred in balochistan during british colonial rule: the 1935 quetta earthquake ,  which devastated quetta ,  and the 1945 balochistan earthquake with its epicentre in the makran region . 
during the period of the british raj from the fall of the durrani empire in 1823, four princely states were recognised and reinforced in balochistan: makran ,  kharan ,  las bela and kalat . 
balochistan contained a chief commissioner's province and four princely states under the british raj . 
in the 15th century ,  mir chakar khan rind became the first sirdar of afghan and pakistani balochistan . 
