the berber languages ,  also known as berber or the amazigh languages  -lrb-  berber name:  ,  ; neo-tifinagh: ⵜⴰⵎⴰⵣⵉⵖⵜ ,  tuareg tifinagh: ⵜⴰⵎⴰⵣⵉⵗⵜ ,  ⵝⴰⵎⴰⵣⵉⵗⵝ ,   ,    -rrb-  ,  are a branch of the afroasiatic language family . 
